{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-index-tsx","path":"/post/yinle-bofangqi","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 925px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/814f4e215ea2233efb57de354b2a1205/8ec0a/wallhaven-4vzej5.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.27705627705628%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/814f4e215ea2233efb57de354b2a1205/a42d1/wallhaven-4vzej5.webp 231w,\n/static/814f4e215ea2233efb57de354b2a1205/a7d21/wallhaven-4vzej5.webp 463w,\n/static/814f4e215ea2233efb57de354b2a1205/31b98/wallhaven-4vzej5.webp 925w,\n/static/814f4e215ea2233efb57de354b2a1205/5c6e0/wallhaven-4vzej5.webp 1388w,\n/static/814f4e215ea2233efb57de354b2a1205/62ac3/wallhaven-4vzej5.webp 1850w,\n/static/814f4e215ea2233efb57de354b2a1205/5a003/wallhaven-4vzej5.webp 2560w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 925px) 100vw, 925px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/814f4e215ea2233efb57de354b2a1205/d4da3/wallhaven-4vzej5.jpg 231w,\n/static/814f4e215ea2233efb57de354b2a1205/ecde2/wallhaven-4vzej5.jpg 463w,\n/static/814f4e215ea2233efb57de354b2a1205/0ff56/wallhaven-4vzej5.jpg 925w,\n/static/814f4e215ea2233efb57de354b2a1205/8d810/wallhaven-4vzej5.jpg 1388w,\n/static/814f4e215ea2233efb57de354b2a1205/aa991/wallhaven-4vzej5.jpg 1850w,\n/static/814f4e215ea2233efb57de354b2a1205/8ec0a/wallhaven-4vzej5.jpg 2560w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 925px) 100vw, 925px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/814f4e215ea2233efb57de354b2a1205/0ff56/wallhaven-4vzej5.jpg\"\n          alt=\"wallhaven-4vzej5\"\n          title=\"wallhaven-4vzej5\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">wallhaven-4vzej5</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>作为一个强迫症，博客没有音乐播放器始终感觉有些遗憾，尽管没怎么写文章</p>\n<p>使用Markdown就代表无法像博客程序那样能快捷方便的添加音乐了，不过这样拦不住我想添加音乐的的想法</p>\n<p>Markdown可以插入Audio标签，虽然支持有限但还是从歌曲中获取的详细的歌曲信息，就是请求也多了几个而已</p>\n<p>使用下面的代码在Markdown文章中插入音乐</p>\n<ul>\n<li>controls 使用controls属性是禁用JavaScript的时候还能继续播放音乐，JavaScript执行的时候会自动将controls关闭</li>\n<li>preload=\"metadata\" 加载基础的音乐信息就够</li>\n<li>title title值存在将直接作为歌曲标题</li>\n<li>artist artist值存在将直接作为歌曲作家</li>\n<li>cover cover值存在将直接作为歌曲封面</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>audio</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">controls</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">preload</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>metadata<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>音乐地址<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>audio</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>注意点：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>加载音乐信息会使用fetch请求，这个受同源策略影响，所以音乐位置必需在支持CORS的服务器或者同域名下</li>\n<li>加载成功后，artist值和cover值将被删除，title值将变为 歌曲名 + 歌曲作家</li>\n<li>当音乐播放时，页面标题将会变为 歌曲名 + 歌曲作家</li>\n</ul>\n<p><audio controls preload=\"metadata\" src=\"https://static.wktrf.com//music/%E9%BA%A6%E6%8C%AF%E9%B8%BF%20-%20%E4%B8%80%E7%94%9F%E5%8F%AA%E7%88%B1%E4%BD%A0%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%BA.mp3\"></audio></p>","id":"c9d6e024-41d4-5976-9ab3-854bd7681b05","fields":{"title":"音乐播放器","tags":[],"category":"记录","date":"2019-08-26T13:52:41+08:00","dateModified":"2019-10-29T03:30:27+08:00","slug":"/post/yinle-bofangqi","status":true,"comment":true},"excerpt":"作为一个强迫症，博客没有音乐播放器始终感觉有些遗憾，尽管没怎么写文章 使用Markdown…"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/post/yinle-bofangqi","prev":{"slug":"/post/nodejsspawn-yongfa","title":"NodeJS Spawn用法","date":"2019-08-23T21:24:48+08:00","category":"笔记","tags":["NodeJS","JavaScript"],"type":"post"},"next":{"slug":"/post/window-zhongduan-zifu-bianma-he-daili-de-shezhi","title":"window终端字符编码和代理的设置","date":"2019-10-27T18:42:00+08:00","category":"教程","tags":["Windows","终端"],"type":"post"}}}}